s securities  exchange commission as an investment advisor under the investment advisers act of  in february  its sec file number is  paulson europe llp an affiliate of paulson  co inc registered with the financial conduct authority in july  its registration number is  similarly paulson asia ltd registered with the sfc in february  its license number is awn investor login   paulson  co inc team approach  paulson  co menu home about paulson  co team approach contact x close paulson  co team approach we believe our people are the key to our success we employ intellectually gifted personable motivated and highly skilled professionals in all areas of our business by encouraging and rewarding teamwork we are able to deliver differentiated products and results our team is comprised of experts with backgrounds in corporate restructurings and credit investment banking law structured finance and specific industry sectors the combination of these skills allows us to analyze events and understand the risks and returns involved in a transaction as a result of our collaborative partnership structure we have benefited from low turnover of senior professionals paulson  co employees have become the largest investors in the funds by consistently reinvesting gains back into the funds and compounding over time similarly a majority of the firm’s total assets have accumulated through compounding performance gains over time about john paulson investor login   paulson  co inc contact us  paulson  co menu home about paulson  co team approach contact x close paulson  co contact us for further information please contact investor relations or    investor login   paulson  co inc john paulson  paulson  co menu home about paulson  co team approach contact x close paulson  co john paulson john paulson is the president and portfolio manager of paulson  co inc “paulson” paulson is an secregistered investment management company specializing in global merger event arbitrage and credit strategies the 