tal analysis to make its investments paulson  co was founded in july  and is based in new york new york  avenue of the americasth floornew york ny united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwpaulsoncocom key executives for paulson  co inc mr john alfred paulson founder president portfolio manager and director age  mr christopher alan bodak chief financial officer mr rufus putnam coes chief operating officer and partner mr andrew hoine director of research age  mr michael waldorf managing director compensation as of fiscal year  paulson  co inc key developments paulson  co inc presents at european gold forum  apr through apr apr   paulson  co inc presents at european gold forum  apr through apr venue park hyatt hotel zurich switzerland presentation date  speakers apr marcelo kim partner victor flores apr marcelo kim partner paulson  co inc presents at th annual international shipping  offshore forum mar  pm mar   paulson  co inc presents at th annual international shipping  offshore forum mar  pm venue metropolitan club one east th street new york united states speakers ty wallach partner paulson  co inc presents at  illiquid financial assets conference mar  am mar   paulson  co inc presents at  illiquid financial assets conference mar  am venue the westin new york grand central new york united states speakers ty wallach partner similar private companies by industry company name region visory llc united states  road partners llc united states t partners llc united states jumpcom inc united states  ontario inc united states recent private companies transactions typedate target mergeracquisition april   akorn inc mergeracquisition february   paulson gold holdings lp private placement december   international tower hill mines ltd request profile update   the information and data displayed in this profile are created and managed by sp global market intelligence a division of sp global bloombergcom does not create or control the content for inquiries please contact sp global 